data.description: **Offer Deadline on Tuesday 02/27 at 3:00 PM**.  Stylish Condo.  Single level, sunken spacious living room, sliding doors that open to a private patio just perfect for morning coffee or afternoon cocktails. The spacious kitchen has new cabinets, quartz counter-top, stainless appliances, tile backsplash.  Two large comfortable bedrooms with plenty of light.  Upgraded bathrooms with beautiful tiles, new flooring,  low monthly HOA,  making this the perfect place to call home. This property is conveniently located in a prime spot in Baltimore-Washington corridor with an easy access to shopping, dining, I-95, Rt -1, Marc train.
